snippet.title: Bardbarian Trailer
snippet.description:
Here is the trailer for our first game called BARDBARIAN, it's available now on iOS/Android/Steam. 

Developer: Treefortress

Treefortress is:
Shawn Blais - Coding
Mike Gaboury - Artwork
Grant Skinner - Overlord

Trailer Music by Red Rum: https://www.facebook.com/redrummetal

Links: 
http://www.treefortress.com
http://www.twitter.com/tree_fortress
http://www.bardbarian.com
